    <p>AIDAH: This will be Anissa's room. She'll never leave.</p>
    <p>ULABY: These good-humored, relatable people are far removed, says professor Evelyn Asultany, from the two kinds of Muslim women you see in scripted television.</p>
    <p>EVELYN ASULTANY: Terrorist or CIA agent.</p>
