    <p>COLE: (Singing) Unforgettable, though near or far.</p>
    <p>(SOUNDBITE OF ARCHIVED BROADCAST)</p>
    <p>COLE: I believe that, you know, he guides me. Dad led by example. You know, he was not a big talker of, oh, you got to do this, you got to do that. That was not him. He led by example. And I watched. I was very observant. And I learned so much from my father. And he continues to be my number one inspiration.</p>
    <p>(SOUNDBITE OF SONG, "UNFORGETTABLE")</p>
    <p>COLE: (Singing) Unforgettable.</p>
