    <p>INSKEEP: Yeah.</p>
    <p>GARZA: There was something a bit different about this. But yes, you're right, they do work very hard to cultivate an image at a local level, almost romanticize what they do.</p>
    <p>INSKEEP: Maybe he began believing his own publicity then.</p>
