    <p>GREENE: And let's just listen to a few of those roles played by Alan Rickman, who passed away. These are a few scenes from "Harry Potter," "Die Hard" and "Dogma."</p>
    <p>(SOUNDBITE OF FILM, "HARRY POTTER AND THE SORCERER'S STONE")</p>
