    <p>HARRIS: I didn't embarrass myself.</p>
    <p>MARTIN: No, you did not at all. You kind of knocked it out of the park. And for playing the puzzle today, you get a WEEKEND EDITION lapel pin and all kinds of puzzle books and games. You can check them out at npr.org/puzzle. And before we let you go, where do you hear us? What's your public radio station?</p>
    <p>HARRIS: My wife, Ann, and I are members of KCFR, 90.1, in Denver.</p>
